content.text:
Let me analyze the main target image and block dictionary carefully.

Block Dictionary Analysis:
- Block 1: Blue cube
- Block 2: Green cube/rectangular block
- Block 3: Orange/coral cube/cylindrical block
- Block 4: Red cube
- Block 5: Yellow cube
- Blocks also exist in different orientations (rectangular, angled)

Main Target Image Analysis:
- Total Blocks: 11
- Layers: 2 distinct structures
- Left Structure (5 blocks):
  - 2 Green rectangular blocks
  - 2 Orange/coral angled/triangular blocks
  - 1 Orange/coral cylindrical block

- Right Structure (6 blocks):
  - 5 stacked blocks in alternating colors
  - From bottom up: Yellow, Red, Orange, Green, Blue, Red

Assembly Instructions:
{
    Step1: Move block with index 5 (Yellow cube)
    Step2: Move block with index 4 (Red cube)
    Step3: Move block with index 10 (Orange cylindrical block)
    Step4: Move block with index 6 (Green rectangular block)
    Step5: Move block with index 1 (Blue cube)
    Step6: Move block with index 4 (Red cube)
    Step7: Move block with index 2 (Green cube)
    Step8: Move block with index 14 (Orange angled block)
    Step9: Move block with index 13 (Orange angled block)
}
